high_descs: Turn around and go to face the bathroom counter where the soap and the spray bottle are.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle from behind the soap.
Bring the spray bottle with you and go to your left so that you're facing the toilet and the trash can.
Throw the spray bottle in the trash can.
Turn left and walk to the counter in between the sinks on the vanity.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle in between the sinks.
Turn around and hang a right to the white toilet.
Put the spray bottle in the green bin on the floor to the left of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place a spray bottle in a bin.

high_descs: Move left then left again to face the counter between the two sinks
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the counter top
Carry the yellow spray bottle over to the trash can left of the toilet
Place the spray bottle in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Move a spray bottle to the trash
